33 Hetuduka, Atītattika
Hetuduka, Atītattika
80.
194Nahetu napaccuppanno dhammo hetussa paccuppannassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
195Ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare samanantare nava, upanissaye nava, natthiyā vigate nava.
